title: 2016 Campeonato Nacional da Guiné-Bissau
text: The 2016 <a href="Campeonato%20Nacional%20da%20Guin%C3%A9-Bissau">Campeonato Nacional da Guiné-Bissau</a> season is the top level of <a href="association%20football">football</a> competition in <a href="Guinea-Bissau">Guinea-Bissau</a>. It began on 16 January 2016. The season was suspended after seven rounds and eventually cancelled for financial reasons on May 6 2016.
